Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,春天到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.84,0:02:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.07,0:02:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.42,0:02:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.63,0:02:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我臉上有沾到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.53,0:02:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有領帶嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.15,0:02:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#24 五代心跳不已!\N和小津江的初吻?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.24,0:03:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.51,0:03:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣應該可以了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.31,0:03:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當了上班族之後\N每天早上都要跟這東西搏鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.08,0:03:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我要去上班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.43,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼又把領帶\N打得歪歪扭扭的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.10,0:03:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.63,0:03:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,領帶打得好不好\N也會影響到升遷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.57,0:03:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,每天都要讓人家操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.94,0:03:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像個小孩子似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.61,0:03:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.71,0:03:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公不要這樣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,不可以一大早就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.02,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.86,0:04:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀,你要出門啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸,有什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.54,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個地方氣氛有點怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.28,0:04:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員的房間?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.08,0:04:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,總覺得不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到您氣色這麼好\N真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,託您的福,腰痛也好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無老伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,還有管理員的爸媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.43,0:04:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,我們在外面等妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.07,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種和諧的氣氛真的很詭異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.61,0:05:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這背後一定有什麼問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.55,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,我記得今天是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.17,0:05:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去給惣一郎掃墓,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪兩家的父母會聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.41,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也不見得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.11,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去年我爸媽就故意找藉口\N沒有來掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.92,0:05:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我傍晚就會回來\N家裡麻煩你們看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.89,0:05:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事,請慢走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們母女應該不會在墳前吵架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,音無老伯脾氣太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.72,0:06:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到那對精明的父母\N他肯定會讓步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N今天不應該答應跟別人約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我又不能跟去掃墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.41,0:06:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有沒有嚇一跳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條領帶好帥氣喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是妳叫我打領帶來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.53,0:07:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.80,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.44,0:07:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想買個東西,陪我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,買東西?只不過是買個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.97,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有需要特地叫我打領帶來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈蜜瓜?領帶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼組合啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳買哈蜜瓜要做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.63,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我來就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.07,0:07:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住宅區?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好帥喔,真有面子真有面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.06,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.13,0:08:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳沒有跟我提這件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.17,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代你就不要害羞了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒有做好心理準備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.91,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然拉我來見妳的家人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.68,0:08:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說妳啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫五代裕作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然來府上打擾,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來蠻老實的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,放心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了來了,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.84,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不好意思\N讓你送這麼貴重的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.34,0:08:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代很有心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕,完全被小津江牽著走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姊姊,你們已經接吻了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你猜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明沒有接吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就老實說嘛\N你們進展到哪裡了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.62,0:09:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葉介
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.69,0:09:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有什麼進展啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少來了啦,別裝蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葉介,你怎麼這麼沒大沒小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.53,0:09:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說不定會變成你的姊夫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係嘛,好痛好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會變成這樣\N連接吻都還沒做耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.64,0:09:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你能誠心誠意地\N和小津江交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟小津江年紀還很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.79,0:09:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.54,0:09:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.81,0:11:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感謝兩位親家來給惣一郎上香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎在天之靈一定很欣慰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.68,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.58,0:11:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去年要不是我老公生病了\N我們也會來上香的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.22,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,沒能經常來看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用為我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.64,0:11:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在一刻館過得很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.24,0:11:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過時間過得真快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.21,0:11:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惣一郎過世都已經兩年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經兩年了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.69,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊,兩年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.16,0:11:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定還對惣一郎念念不忘吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是還好啦\N倒是響子好像還很思念他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.31,0:12:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過也不能讓響子\N就這樣守寡下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.75,0:12:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照這樣下去不是辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還這麼年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.76,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是儘早跟音無家脫離關係\N重新開始比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是不是跟音無親家\N說了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有,還沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.25,0:12:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?\N為什麼你要說這種話呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.95,0:12:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我重新開始什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是叫我忘記惣一郎嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.41,0:13:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前丈夫過世的話,墓碑上\N都會用紅字寫上妻子的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.71,0:13:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫著“未亡人”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.05,0:13:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是還沒有死的妻子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.09,0:13:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,未亡人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.22,0:13:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,這樣是不對的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是還沒死,而是還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老婆,這番話好感人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說得真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.51,0:14:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,妳一定要忘了惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.52,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我身為音無家的一份子\N讓你覺得很困擾嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.23,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不會呢\N我反而覺得很慶幸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.17,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳如此深愛著惣一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是妳的人生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.14,0:15:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請暫時再讓我任性下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.41,0:15:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道妳不明白\N親家公的一片苦心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.85,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸說的話\N在理論上我非常瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.02,0:15:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.06,0:15:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子,今後妳打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.96,0:15:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直到明白自己該怎麼做之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.60,0:15:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想繼續冠著惣一郎的姓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳怎麼這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬一年紀越來越大\N無法再婚怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.98,0:15:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳還沒有喜歡的人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.38,0:15:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎麼樣?響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,你們在胡說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡可是惣一郎的墳前耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.32,0:15:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爸跟我媽好像都很喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這倒是還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.06,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是這樣正式的\N把我介紹給妳家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.53,0:16:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直就像什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.00,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認識對方的父母也很重要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,畢竟結婚也是\N兩個家族之間的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結婚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.07,0:16:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會有這種結論?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.01,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得先見過對方的父母\N以後交往起來會比較輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方的父母啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有辦法跟響子的父母\N順利相處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.53,0:17:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能跟他們順利相處嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事,我在自言自語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,妳聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣順序好像不太對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.48,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順序?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.71,0:17:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照理說,應該先要有穩定的\N男女交往後,才見對方的父母吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也對\N我們什麼都還沒做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你什麼都不做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.87,0:17:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該做呢?還是不該做呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吻一下,應該…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.65,0:17:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到手的肉哪有不吃的道理呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟敢非禮我女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.06,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽我說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.46,0:18:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿出你的誠意來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到區公所去辦結婚手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.43,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們小津江年紀還很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是吻一下而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是吻一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.84,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是抱著這種\N隨便的心情,親我女兒的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽,請妳幫我說說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.48,0:18:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老公,你應該高興\N五代他叫我媽媽了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.42,0:18:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於明白啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.19,0:18:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,也叫我一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.73,0:18:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點叫他爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.65,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣我就能放心跟三鷹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.59,0:19:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.56,0:19:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的,響子,妳誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.41,0:19:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊,有人在窗戶那裡偷看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭,一定是我弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪,可能是我看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我傍晚就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.14,0:20:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我傍晚就會回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五代你到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.03,0:20:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小津江,我跟妳說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.34,0:21:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些人一起去掃墓\N不可能風平浪靜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.22,0:21:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她回來的時候一定會心力交瘁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明明知道會有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.89,0:21:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我竟然去跟別人約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.06,0:21:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我總是這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明很擔心妳\N卻沒有馬上飛奔到妳身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.96,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,響子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.21,0:21:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.91,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼忙都幫不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我無能為力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我能做的事\N只有安慰妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.00,0:21:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.33,0:22:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這孩子真不懂事\N音無親家都已經那麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.23,0:22:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就順水推舟嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.00,0:22:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們很煩耶\N同樣的事要我說幾次才甘願啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.87,0:22:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說都說不聽的人\N明明是妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.01,0:22:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要跟著我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.25,0:22:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳知不知道\N我們為什麼要這麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.12,0:22:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道,你們這些閒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.22,0:22:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恢復舊姓有什麼不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.55,0:22:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳很煩耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.12,0:22:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.79,0:22:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要演悲劇女主角\N演到什麼時候啊,太難看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.59,0:22:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼大聲,大家都在看耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.83,0:22:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫妳說不聽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不聽的是你們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.97,0:22:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經是個大人了\N要怎麼過日子是我的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對父母來說\N孩子不論長到多大都是孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.01,0:22:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說點意見有什麼不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.54,0:22:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也要適可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.91,0:22:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這麼做真的是為妳好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.35,0:22:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在過得很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.02,0:22:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.85,0:22:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寡婦哪裡幸福了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.35,0:22:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是價值觀的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.69,0:22:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們才是不要老是一付\N悲劇父母的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.69,0:23:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為你們自己的幸福著想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.79,0:23:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.83,0:23:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來想要有個男孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.30,0:23:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望有個理想的女婿\N這有什麼不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.60,0:23:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想再婚也無所謂\N跟我們回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.94,0:23:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.67,0:23:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個不懂羞恥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.77,0:23:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然對父母說吵死了\N妳這是什麼態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.48,0:23:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了就是吵死了
